4. Important Parameters
dirb URL
-w → custom wordlist
-X → extensions
-r → do NOT recurse
-S → silent mode
-o → save output

----

5. Usage Examples
dirb https://site.com /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt
dirb https://site.com -X .php,.html

